          | ...
      .device-spacer(style="height:30px").stop-scroll-device
      .full-width
        .important-note
          p If you don't want your Navbar/Toolbar became visible when scroll reaches end of the page, then you need to disable <b>showBarsOnPageScrollEnd</b> parameter on <a href="init-app.html">App initialization</a>
      